        {
            "title": "在宅急症照護保單鎖定三大感染症 國壽、富壽、南山3家申請試辦中",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\" data-component=\"blocks\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"在宅急症照護保單鎖定三大感染症 國壽、富壽、南山3家申請試辦中\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"538\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/lo/mysterio/api/75a25f13e2465cf8fb41bf57377f5cb5a1697a8d61e1e1967b455ac5c24e69af/lightyear_networkapi/resizefill_w960;quality_80;format_webp/https:%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fcnyes_hk_559%2F7f170b52747d0b501048df8dfa89dc2e\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">在宅急症照護保單鎖定三大感染症 國壽、富壽、南山3家申請試辦中</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%A8%E5%AE%85%E6%80%A5%E7%97%87%E7%85%A7%E8%AD%B7%E4%BF%9D%E5%96%AE%E9%8E%96%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E7%97%87-%E5%9C%8B%E5%A3%BD-%E5%AF%8C%E5%A3%BD-%E5%8D%97%E5%B1%B13%E5%AE%B6%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E8%A9%A6%E8%BE%A6%E4%B8%AD-162415164.html",
